content:
{
  "name": "fakexy",
  "version": "2.1.0",
  "description": "A wrapper over fakexy.com",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "./main.js",
  "exports": "./main.js",
  "scripts": {
    "test": "mocha",
    "docs": "esdoc"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/kartikanand/fakexy.js.git"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "fakexy",
    "fake",
    "address",
    "fake address generator",
    "fake names",
    "fake cards",
    "faker",
    "fake phone numbers",
    "fake zip codes"
  ],
  "author": "Kartik Anand",
  "license": "MIT",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/kartikanand/fakexy.js/issues"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/kartikanand/fakexy.js#readme",
  "devDependencies": {
    "chai": "^4.3.4",
    "chai-as-promised": "^7.1.1",
    "esdoc": "^1.1.0",
    "esdoc-standard-plugin": "^1.0.0",
    "eslint": "^8.5.0",
    "eslint-config-airbnb-base": "^15.0.0",
    "eslint-config-prettier": "^8.3.0",
    "eslint-plugin-import": "^2.25.3",
    "eslint-plugin-mocha": "^10.0.3",
    "eslint-plugin-prettier": "^4.0.0",
    "mocha": "^9.1.3",
    "prettier": "^2.5.1"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "axios": "^0.24.0",
    "cheerio": "^1.0.0-rc.10"
  }
}
